                                                <div class="text-danger text-warning">1. The above all 6 fields are mendatory field for subject selection in 12th Standard and Last 7th row is the extra subject. <br /><br></div>
                                            <div class="text-danger text-warning">2. Student Can edit Total Marks as according to his/her Intermediate MarksSheet. University shall not be responsible for any kind of discrepancy. </div>

